\f0\fs24 \cf0 * Permission needed to see the 'Permissions' link:\ \ - site.upd\ \ * Permission(s) needed to see Instructor View:\ \ - Add assignments AND/OR\ - Edit assignments AND/OR \ - Remove assignments AND/OR\ - View Submissions\ \ In the absence of one or more of the above permissions, the system will display the student view to the user.\ \ * Permission(s) needed to see list of assignments in Instructor View:\ \ - Add assignments AND/OR \ - Edit assignments AND/OR\ - Remove assignments AND/OR\ - View Submissions\ \ By default, the system will display assignments that have been released to all and/or to hish/her assigned groups. The system will not display assignments that have been released to a group of which he/she is not a member.\ \ If the user has one or more of the above permissions and the user has the 'View all groups' permission, then the system will display all assignments to the user regardless of which group the assignment has been released to.\ \ * Permission needed to see 'Add' link:\ \ - Add assignments\ \ * Permission needed to see 'Edit' link:\ \ - Edit assignments\ \ By default, the system will display the 'Edit' link to a user for assignments that have been released to his/her assigned groups. The system will not display the 'Edit' link for assignments that have been released to all students unless the user has the 'Edit assignments' permission and the 'View all groups' permission, then the system will display the 'Edit' link for all assignments.}

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\cocoartf1038\cocoasubrtf110 {\fonttbl\f0\fswiss\fcharset0 Helvetica;} {\colortbl;\red255\green255\blue255;} \pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\ql\qnatural\pardirnatural
\f0\fs24 \cf0 * Permission needed to see 'Duplicate' link:\ \ - Edit assignments\ \ By default, the system will display the 'Duplicate' link to a user for assignments that have been released to his/her groups. The system will not display the 'Duplicate' link for assignments that have been released to all unless the user has the 'Edit assignments' permission and the 'View all groups' permission, then the system will display the 'Duplicate' link for all assignments.\ \ * Permission needed to see 'Grade' or 'Provide Feedback' link:\ \ - View Submissions\ \ By default, the system will display the 'Grade' or 'Provide Feedback' link to a user if the assignment has been released to all or to his/her assigned groups. The system will not display the 'Grade' or 'Provide Feedback' link if the assignment has been released to a group of which the user is not a member unless the user has the 'View Submissions' permission and the 'View all groups' permission, then the system will display the 'Grade' and/or 'Provide Feedback' link for all assignments.\ \ * Permission needed to see 'In/New' column:\ \ - View Submissions\ \ By default, the system will display a value in the 'In/New' column to a user if the assignment has been released to all or to his/her assigned groups. The system will display a non-clickable 'N/A' value in the 'In/New' column for assignments that have been released to a group of which the user is not a member unless the user has the 'View Submissions' permission and the 'View all groups' permission, then the system will display the 'In/New' column for all assignments.\ \ * Permission needed to see 'Remove' column:\ \ - Remove Assignments\ \ By default, the system will display a checkbox in the 'Remove' column to a user is the assignment has been released to his/her assigned groups. The system will not display a checkbox in the 'Remove' column if the assignment has been released to all unless the user has the 'Remove Assignments' permission and the 'View all Groups' permission, then the system will display a checkbox for all assignments.\ \ }

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\cocoartf1038\cocoasubrtf110 {\fonttbl\f0\fswiss\fcharset0 Helvetica;} {\colortbl;\red255\green255\blue255;} \pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\ql\qnatural\pardirnatural
\f0\fs24 \cf0 * Permission needed to receive submission notifications:\ \ - View Submissions\ \ By default, the system will send a submission notification to a user if a submission was made by a student in one of his/her assigned group(s). If the user has the 'View Submissions' permission and the 'View All Groups' permission, then the user will receive submission notifications for all student submissions.\ \ * Permission needed to see 'Retract Grades' link:\ \ - gradebook.editAssignments\ \ * Permission needed to see 'Retract All Student Feedback' link:\ \ - View Submissions\ \ By default, the system will only retract feedback for the students in a user's assigned groups unless the user has the 'View Submissions' permission and the 'View All Groups' permission, then the system will retract feedback for all students.\ \ * Permission needed to see 'Download All' link:\ \ - View Submissions\ \ By default, the system will only download the submissions for the students in a user's assigned groups unless the user has the 'View Submissions' permission and the 'View All Groups' permission, then the system will download all student submissions.\ \ * Permission needed to see AssignmentName-SiteID.csv file in Download folder:\ \ - gradebook.gradeAll OR\ - gradebook.gradeSection\ \ Users with the gradebook.gradeAll permission will see all students in the site listed in the AssignmentName-SiteID.csv file. Users with the gradebook.gradeSection permission will only see students in his/her assigned group(s) in this file unless grader permissions have been set, in which case those permissions would override the gradebook.gradeSection permission.\ \ * Permission needed to see 'Upload Grades and Feedback' link:\ \ - View Submissions}

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\cocoartf1038\cocoasubrtf110 {\fonttbl\f0\fswiss\fcharset0 Helvetica;} {\colortbl;\red255\green255\blue255;} \pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\ql\qnatural\pardirnatural
\f0\fs24 \cf0 * Permission needed to upload feedback:\ \ By default, the system will only allow a user to upload feedback for the students in a user's assigned groups unless the user has the 'View Submissions' permission and the 'View All Groups' permission, then the system will allow the user to upload feedback for all students.\ \ * Permission needed to upload grades:\ \ - gradebook.gradeAll OR\ - gradebook.gradeSection\ \ Users with the gradebook.gradeAll permission will have permission to upload grades and comments for all students in the site. Users with the gradebook.gradeSection permission will only have permission to upload grades and comments for students in his/her assigned groups unless grader permissions have been set, in which case those permissions would override the gradebook.gradeSection permission.\ \ * Permission needed to see 'All Sections/Groups' in View drop-down on View Graded Submissions (VGS-1) or View Ungraded Submissions (VUS-1) screen:\ \ - View Submissions AND\ - View All Groups\ \ If a user does not have the 'View All Groups' permission, then the user will see his/her assigned groups listed in the View drop-down.\ \ * Permission needed to see list of students:\ \ - View Submissions\ \ By default, the system will display the students in the user's assigned groups unless the user has the 'View Submissions' permission and the 'View All Groups' permission, then the system will display all students in the site.\ \ * Permissions needed to see grade in 'Grade' column:\ \ - gradebook.gradeAll OR\ - gradebook.gradeSection\ \ Users with the gradebook.gradeAll permission will have permission to view grades for all students in the site. Users with the gradebook.gradeSection permission will only have permission to view grades for students in his/her assigned groups.\ \ Please note that the system will be looking at the 'View Submissions' and 'View All Groups' permissions to determine which students to display to the user and then the system will look for the gradebook.gradeAll or gradebook.gradeSection permission to determine if the user has permission to view the grades for those students.\ \ }

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\cocoartf1038\cocoasubrtf110 {\fonttbl\f0\fswiss\fcharset0 Helvetica;} {\colortbl;\red255\green255\blue255;} \pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\ql\qnatural\pardirnatural
\f0\fs24 \cf0 * Permissions needed to see 'Apply grade to all ungraded' text box:\ \ - gradebook.gradeAll OR\ - gradebook.gradeSection\ \ Users with the gradebook.gradeAll permission will have permission to apply a grade for all ungraded students. Users with the gradebook.gradeSection permission will have permission to apply a grade to the ungraded students in his/her assigned groups.\ \ Please note that the system will be looking at the 'View Submissions' and 'View All Groups' permissions to determine which students to display to the user and then the system will look for the gradebook.gradeAll or gradebook.gradeSection permission to determine if the user has permission to view the grades for those students.\ \ * Permission needed to see Gradebook Details section for all students on View Student's Submission screen (VSS-1):\ \ - gradebook.gradeAll OR\ - gradebook.gradeSection\ \ Users with the gradebook.gradeAll permission will have permission to view and edit the Gradebook Details section for all students. Users with the gradebook.gradeSection permission will have permission to view and edit the Gradebook Details section for all students in his/her assigned groups.\ \ Please note that the system will be looking at the 'View Submissions' and 'View All Groups' permissions to determine which students to display to the user and then the system will look for the gradebook.gradeAll or gradebook.gradeSection permission to determine if the user has permission to view the grades for those students.}
